LLC_BI__Loan__c

LLC_BI__Current_LTV__c
Current LTV
Formula (Percent)
true
false
This field is automatically populated via a formula. It stores the current LTV of the loan based on its Collateral Mgmt records. If the Product Feature is NOT a Line of Credit, or if the Product Feature does not exist, this is the formula: (Principal Balance + Total Prior Lien Amount from all Collateral)/ Collateral Value from all Collateral. If the Product Feature is a Line of Credit, this is the formula: Original Loan Amount / (Collateral Value from all Collateral - Total Prior Lien Amount from all Collateral)
